 TMUX CHEATSHEET                              q to close

 PANES
  Ctrl-b %       Split vertical
  Ctrl-b "       Split horizontal
  Ctrl-b z       Zoom/unzoom pane
  Ctrl-b x       Close pane
  Ctrl-b o       Next pane
  Ctrl-b q       Show pane numbers (press number to jump)

 SESSIONS
  Ctrl-b a       New session (prompt for name)
  Ctrl-b s       Browse & switch sessions
  Ctrl-b (  )    Previous / next session
  Ctrl-b L       Toggle last session
  Ctrl-b $       Rename session
  Ctrl-b k       Kill current session (with confirmation)
  Ctrl-b d       Detach session

 OTHER
  Ctrl-b b       Toggle status bar
  Ctrl-b [       Scroll mode (q to exit)
